In Quality Rating Codes (PQA) we can set codes useful for a weighted valuation on the vendor's supply quality:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000569-0/36ProductQualityAssurance-ENU.png"><br>

The quality of the supply is linked to the "gravity" of Non-Compliance. Only the user who is responsible for the PQA knows whether any Non-Compliance is serious or not. Let's see how.